channel.title: The Null Team
channel.description:
Yo i am looking to make a team to identify all the globalobject nulls.
incase ur wondering nulls are items that cannot be examined or used (nothing happens when u right click them)
usualy things like walls .floor tiles, and roofs.
i wanna find about 50+ people each to identify 100 nulls each. PLEASE GIVE A VERY GOOD DISCRIPTION OF THE NULL such as (1221 - wall - found at the varock castle has a grey stone pattern.)
please nothing like (1221 - wall - this looks kool.) or (1221 - dont know what this is.) or (1221 - nothing.)
if we could identify every null imagine what kind of stuff we could do in runescape. totaly re design it thats what.
post if ur interested or if u have identities of nulls just post em here.
creds in the list to everyone who helps out.
